text: Square Window is a promotional 3" CD EP by Squarepusher, distributed only with pre-orders of Ultravisitor from Warp Records' online store. The five songs on this EP were also included on the second disc of the Japanese version of Ultravisitor. ==Track listing== #"Square Window" – 5:01 #"Abacus 2" – 5:13 #"Venus No. 17" – 6:44 #"Itti-Fack" – 0:44 #"Melt 14.6" – 1:16 ==References== *Discogs entry Category:2004 EPs Category:Squarepusher EPs
title: Square Window
